sentinel.led
Class PrimitiveEventHandle

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--sentinel.led.EventHandle
        |
        +--sentinel.led.PrimitiveEventHandle
public class PrimitiveEventHandle
extends EventHandle

This class denotes a primitive event handle used for creating composite events and rules. It is used in composite event creation and rule creation API. The event handle is also used to insert the parameters of a primitive event and raise the event through raiseBeginEvent() or raiseEndEvent() API.
